; AutoCAD Script File - Export Operations
; Exports drawing in multiple formats for distribution

; Set file dialog off for batch operations
FILEDIA 0

; Export current layout to PDF
-EXPORTPDF _C _Y

; Export all layouts to PDF
-EXPORTPDF _ALL _Y  

; Export to DWF
-EXPORTDWF _ALL _Y

; Save as older AutoCAD version (2018)
SAVEAS _DWG _2018

; Turn file dialog back on
FILEDIA 1

QSAVE